{"tid":374330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲男與後母亂倫　遭兩兄弟扯斷陰莖失血死","createTime":"2017-08-25T15:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T20:01:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a54a2363ea3367596b76abdaa2e53349e27e38d0","tid":374330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"07月23日(日) 19:20<br />\n非洲國家津巴布韋一名34歲男子，早前被兩名同父異母的兄弟發現與他們的母親性交，二人目睹到勃然大怒，一怒之下出手扯斷該名男子的陰莖，令他失血過多至死。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌殺人的2名弟弟分別是24歲的哈德來福（Hardlife Chimoko Sithole）和20歲的羅伊德（Lloyd Mukukuzi），他們早前發現哥哥夏含巴（Siyahamba Mukukuzi）在一片草地上與母親交歡，隨即拿出皮帶抽打夏含巴，並伸手扯斷夏含巴的陰莖。<br />\n<br />\n哈德來福及羅伊德事後被捕，早前上庭受審，二人否認控罪，最終被判入獄15年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170723/bknint-20170723192052556-0723_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170723%2Fbknint-20170723192052556-0723_17011_001.html&d=7%2BaaaxUrS%2Fp8pEpoLvQwP9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8d75ac7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170723/bknint-20170723192052556-0723_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f5a265d5b350489975c6d7786e8409699707a5f","tid":374330,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f558aec70495062481b7e8f58c62301ac213b59","tid":374330,"uid":106544,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"夏含巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96540f7675007685a82433500bdcffb34f2a4c85","tid":374330,"uid":57705,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e44e009c042c98344c6a2ad7af23128014534e6","tid":374330,"uid":25635,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"自己無份屌都唔洗咁下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 